# LinkMenu Component Rule

The [LinkMenu.vue](mdc:src/components/menus/LinkMenu/LinkMenu.vue) component follows shadcn-vue conventions:

- It is a single file component (SFC) in the `src/components/menus/LinkMenu` directory.
- Uses Radix Vue primitives for menu logic and accessibility.
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling and utility classes.
- Handles link-related actions and UI in a modular way.

For menu and popover best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Dropdown Menu documentation](mdc:https:/www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/dropdown-menu).



